            "title": "映恩生物登場初段飆逾倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今日登場的新股映恩生物(09606)，於開市初段顯著造好，最高曾見222元，較招股價94.6元高1.35倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"映恩生物招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/09606-IPO.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"映恩生物招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/09606-IPO.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">映恩生物招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至於上午10時13分，該股報204.4元，仍較招股價高1.16倍；早前低位181元，也高於招股價91.33%。開市不足45分鐘成交已達15.7億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該股在港公開售股部份錄115.14倍認購，國際配售部份亦獲13.52倍認購。在港公開發售認購1手(即100股)，中籤率為80.01%，認購10手(即1000股)可穩獲分配1手。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14855444-%e6%98%a0%e6%81%a9%e7%94%9f%e7%89%a9%e7%99%bb%e5%a0%b4%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e9%a3%86%e9%80%be%e5%80%8d",
